# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:14
translate portuguese danaq1_99fc1d8c:

    # cw "I've been wondering something. How did you get hired by Mrs. Mills in the first place?"
    cw "Tenho andado a pensar numa coisa. Como é que foste contratada pela Sra. Mills, afinal?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:15
translate portuguese danaq1_64c0ab66:

    # cw "I saw so many women go in there to interview with her and she turned them all down."
    cw "Vi tantas mulheres a entrarem lá para se entrevistarem com ela e ela recusou-as a todas."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:16
translate portuguese danaq1_d54edc42:

    # cw "But you go in for five minutes and she gives you the job, works with you on school hours, and even lets you drive one of the company cars."
    cw "Mas tu entras por cinco minutos e ela dá-te o emprego, adapta-se ao teu horário escolar e até te deixa conduzir um dos carros da empresa."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:17
translate portuguese danaq1_dc94d298:

    # cw "It's pretty weird."
    cw "É bastante estranho."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:18
translate portuguese danaq1_b4025d52:

    # pc "I guess I make a good first impression."
    pc "Acho que causo uma boa primeira impressão."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:20
translate portuguese danaq1_6ef829be:

    # cw "Well, that's true."
    cw "Bem, isso é verdade."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:21
translate portuguese danaq1_20e8900d:

    # pc "She seemed like she was getting pretty desperate too."
    pc "Ela também parecia estar a ficar bastante desesperada."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:23
translate portuguese danaq1_4b2324cd:

    # cw "Yeah, I think she's desperate for {i}something{/i}."
    cw "Sim, acho que ela está desesperada por {i}alguma coisa{/i}."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:25
translate portuguese danaq1_7d7f5156:

    # cw "She seems like she hasn't gotten laid in {i}years{/i}."
    cw "Parece que ela não faz sexo há {i}anos{/i}."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:27
translate portuguese danaq1_e7eda259:

    # pc "You'd be surprised."
    pc "Ficarias surpreendido."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:29
translate portuguese danaq1_e2c67529:

    # pc "I think you're probably right."
    pc "Acho que provavelmente tens razão."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:30
translate portuguese danaq1_8b413a5a:

    # pc "How did you get {i}your{/i} job, if she seems to only want to hire guys?"
    pc "Como é que conseguiste o teu emprego, se ela parece querer contratar apenas homens?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:32
translate portuguese danaq1_041adc8d:

    # cw "Oh, Mr. Gonzales hired me, not Mrs. Mills."
    cw "Oh, foi o Sr. Gonzales que me contratou, não a Sra. Mills."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:33
translate portuguese danaq1_2d010a53:

    # cw "I started as his assistant, kind of like what you do for Mrs. Mills."
    cw "Comecei como assistente dele, mais ou menos como o que fazes para a Sra. Mills."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:34
translate portuguese danaq1_7d98ce90:

    # cw "But when he started working at the courthouse more often, he promoted me to the office manager and hired a new assistant."
    cw "Mas quando ele começou a trabalhar no tribunal com mais frequência, promoveu-me a gerente do escritório e contratou um novo assistente."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:36
translate portuguese danaq1_1a5ff095:

    # cw "I honestly enjoyed the assistant job more."
    cw "Sinceramente, gostava mais do trabalho de assistente."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:37
translate portuguese danaq1_e4e66e6e:

    # cw "It felt like I was really doing stuff, you know? Almost like I was a lawyer."
    cw "Sentia que estava realmente a fazer coisas, percebes? Quase como se fosse uma advogada."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:38
translate portuguese danaq1_b6b44d2b:

    # cw "Now I just answer phones, manage schedules, and file paperwork."
    cw "Agora, limito-me a atender o telefone, gerir agendas e arquivar documentos."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:40
translate portuguese danaq1_bf842641:

    # cw "But this job pays more and Terry didn't like me being alone with Mr. Gonzales so much."
    cw "Mas este emprego paga melhor e o Terry não gostava muito de me ver sozinha com o Sr. Gonzales."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq1.rpy:41
translate portuguese danaq1_9372bbc6:

    # cw "I wouldn't have ever done anything with Mr. Gonzales, but Terry was so insecure."
    cw "Eu nunca teria feito nada com o Sr. Gonzales, mas o Terry era tão inseguro."

